			<div id="main-content">
				<h1>Dynamic Machine Corporation</h1>
<h2>Geared for Success</h2>
<p>
  Dynamic Machine Corporation of Winnipeg, Manitoba is a modern industrial manufacturing, repair and supply
  company with a fully-equipped machine shop capable of dealing with projects of any size.  Since
  1970 Dynamic Machine has been serving national and international clients both by building and repairing all types of 
  custom and general production machinery and by selling, servicing and repairing all brands of hydraulic
  and pneumatic equipment. Staffed by more than 80 dedicated professionals, including machinists, mechanics,
  welders, engineers, parts specialists and support staff.  The company features a parts department stocking
  an extensive selection of Parker hydraulic parts, pneumatic parts, custom hoses and fittings along with
  Atlas Copco Compressors and Equipment and related supplies.
</p>

<h2>A Dynamic Group of Companies</h2>
<p>
  The divisions of the Dynamic Machine Corporation – which include Dynamic Machine Shop, Dynamic Fluid Power,
  Hose Doctor, Dynamic Online Parts, Dynamic Compressors, Westcan Hydraulic Lines, and K&S Tool and Die – provide onsite and shop service
  to our customers across Manitoba, Saskatchewan, Northwestern Ontario and the Northern United States.
</p>

<h2>Dynamic Machine: Professional - Innovative - Reliable</h2>

